### Welcome to EXPED IT
EXPED IT is an information technology business specialising in product development of operations research software and algorithms.

### Support or Contact
If you'd like someone to contact you please contact us at public@expedit.com.au or contact Andrew (@dioptre) on +61400970789. To leave us feedback, please use our feedback form at http://intranet.expedit.com.au/home/feedback.
